</h3><p>Sim. Esse ï¿½ o objetivo da codificaï¿½ï¿½o em entidades.</p><h3>ï¿½ instantï¿½neo?</h3><p>Sim. O resultado ï¿½ local e imediato.</p></div></div></main><script>function encHTML(){const d=document.createElement('div');d.textContent=document.getElementById('he-in').value;document.getElementById('he-out').value=d.innerHTML} function clearHE(){document.getElementById('he-in').value='';document.getElementById('he-out').value='';} function copyHE(b){copyToClipboard(document.getElementById('he-out').value,b)}</script><?php ns_render_page_end(); ?>
